</taxonomicName>
(Strasser, 1962) gen. nov., comb. nov., ♂ from Ponora Cave, Bulgaria, left gonopod (NMNHS-10813) 
<emphasis id="56C0B550B242147C4523F2AA924B8B3D" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A, B</emphasis>
mesal views 
<emphasis id="C6464291D2E336BC79E5062DF9777E5E" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">C</emphasis>
antero-distal view 
<emphasis id="E4EB2C37610DE9997DC84BB9590948F7" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">D</emphasis>
distal view 
<emphasis id="071B5775A6990DDA44B2EE921400C0B5" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">E</emphasis>
lateral view 
<emphasis id="88B92B006ABFA06450511BDF0AEF7C2C" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">F</emphasis>
anterior view. Abbreviations: 
